column5: Nate popped the first fish not long after the starting bell, but it was a perch that didn’t quite make eight inches.   A few minutes later, Johnny popped an ‘eye that went for first fish.  Within two or three hours we had all iced fish.  We also experienced some double-header action this day.   It was shaping up to be a great trip and we were drinking to celebrate!               TBC...
